    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Synapse Platform是核心系统，定位是AI应用构建器。另外我们依赖两个外部系统：OpenAI作为大模型提供商，还有Stripe做计费。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "syn",
        "oai",
        "stripe"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把这四个元素先放上去：Developer（Person）、Synapse Platform（System）、OpenAI和Stripe（都作为外部系统）。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "dev",
        "syn",
